<item>
            <title>[LOG4J2-2453] Missing dependency to log4j-slf4j18-impl in log4j-bom</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2453</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to &lt;a href=&quot;https://logging.apache.org/log4j/2.x/log4j-slf4j-impl/index.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://logging.apache.org/log4j/2.x/log4j-slf4j-impl/index.html&lt;/a&gt; there are two SLF4J to Log4j adapters provided since release 2.11.1:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;log4j-slf4j-impl for SLF4J 1.7.x releases or older&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;log4j-slf4j18-impl for SLF4J 1.8.x releases or newer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;When I use the following snippet in my (corporate parent) pom.xml&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&amp;lt;dependencyManagement&amp;gt;
 &#160;&amp;lt;dependencies&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;
&#160;&#160; &#160;  &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.logging.log4j&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;
  &#160;&#160; &#160;&amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;log4j-bom&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;
&#160;&#160;   &#160;&amp;lt;version&amp;gt;2.11.1&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;
&#160;&#160; &#160;  &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;import&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt;
  &#160;&#160; &#160;&amp;lt;type&amp;gt;pom&amp;lt;/type&amp;gt;
    &amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;
  &amp;lt;/dependencies&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/dependencyManagement&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I can omit the version numbers in my pom.xml for the Log4J components I&apos;m using:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;(...)
&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;
&#160; &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.logging.log4j&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;
&#160; &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;log4j-core&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;

&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;
&#160; &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.logging.log4j&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;
&#160; &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;log4j-slf4j-impl&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;

&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;
 &#160;&amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;org.apache.logging.log4j&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;
&#160; &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;log4j-jul&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;
(...)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This only works for the artifact &lt;tt&gt;log4j-slf4j-impl&lt;/tt&gt;, but NOT for&#160;&lt;tt&gt;log4j-slf4j18-impl&lt;/tt&gt; which isn&apos;t contained / managed in the BOM.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
